<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{{ title }} | crustaceans.sh</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --sand: #f6efe2;
      --cream: #fffaf1;
      --foam: #f5fbff;
      --sea: #5d8fa3;
      --deep-sea: #28576b;
      --coral: #d87959;
      --ink: #26343c;
      --coffee: #6d4a38;
      --sun: #f4c96b;
      --shadow: rgba(37, 53, 66, 0.16);
    }

    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      :root {
        --sand: #1a1f24;
        --cream: #232a30;
        --foam: #2d353d;
        --sea: #5d8fa3;
        --deep-sea: #8ab4c7;
        --coral: #d87959;
        --ink: #e8ebe8;
        --coffee: #b8a595;
        --sun: #f4c96b;
        --shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
      }
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 2rem 1rem 3rem;
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(244, 201, 107, 0.12), transparent 24%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(93, 143, 163, 0.1), transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, var(--sand) 0%, #2a3038 42%, #1f242a 100%);
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }

    .frame {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 1.2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.72), rgba(255,255,255,0.4));
      border-radius: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 24px 64px var(--shadow);
    }

    .sheet {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--cream), #fff5e8);
      border: 2px solid #ead8b8;
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 2rem;
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 10px rgba(255,255,255,0.34);
    }

    
    .theme-toggle {
      position: absolute;
      top: 2rem;
      right: 2rem;
      background: var(--cream);
      border: 1px solid rgba(109, 74, 56, 0.2);
      border-radius: 50%;
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, background 0.3s ease;
      z-index: 10;
    }
    .theme-toggle:hover { transform: scale(1.1); }
.coffee-ring {
      position: absolute;
      right: 2.8rem;
      top: 1.2rem;
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 6px solid rgba(109, 74, 56, 0.22);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 12px rgba(109, 74, 56, 0.05);
      transform: rotate(-10deg);
      opacity: 0.55;
      mix-blend-mode: multiply;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .content { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

    .site-nav {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.55rem;
      margin: 0 0 1.2rem;
    }

    .site-nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 0.42rem 0.78rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(93, 143, 163, 0.10);
      border: 1px solid rgba(40, 87, 107, 0.12);
      font: 600 0.92rem/1.1 system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--deep-sea);
    }

    h1, h2, h3 { color: var(--deep-sea); margin-top: 0; }
    h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.4rem; margin-top: 2rem; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(109,74,56,0.15); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    p, li { line-height: 1.75; color: var(--ink); }
    ul { padding-left: 1.2rem; }
    li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

    .entry { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .entry-date {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(93, 143, 163, 0.12);
      padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font: 700 0.7rem/1 system-ui, sans-serif;
      color: var(--deep-sea);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }
    .entry-title { font-weight: 700; color: var(--deep-sea); margin: 0.4rem 0 0.3rem; }

    .stamp {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(244, 201, 107, 0.28);
      padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font: 700 0.75rem/1 system-ui, sans-serif;
      color: var(--coffee);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }

    hr {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px dashed rgba(109, 74, 56, 0.2);
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }
  
    html.dark body {
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(244, 201, 107, 0.08), transparent 24%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(93, 143, 163, 0.06), transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1f24 0%, #1f242a 100%);
    }
    html.dark .frame {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(35, 42, 48, 0.8), rgba(35, 42, 48, 0.5));
    }
    html.dark .sheet {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #232a30, #2d353d);
      border-color: rgba(184, 165, 149, 0.2);
    }
    html.dark .site-nav a {
      background: rgba(93, 143, 163, 0.15);
      border-color: rgba(138, 180, 199, 0.2);
      color: #8ab4c7;
    }
    html.dark h1, html.dark h2, html.dark h3 { color: #8ab4c7; }
    html.dark .eyebrow, html.dark .mini {
      background: rgba(244, 201, 107, 0.15);
      color: #b8a595;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="frame">
    <article class="sheet">
      <div class="coffee-ring"></div>
      <div class="content">
        <nav class="site-nav" aria-label="Site navigation">
          <a href="/">Postcard rack</a>
          <a href="/which-claw/">Which Claw?</a>
          <a href="/first-routes/">First Setup Routes</a>
          <a href="/recommendations/">Tuning the Claws</a>
          <a href="/community-currents/">Community Currents</a>
          <a href="/about/">About</a>
        </nav>
        <button class="theme-toggle" onclick="toggleTheme()" aria-label="Toggle dark mode">☀️</button>


        <span class="stamp">In progress</span>
        <h1>Changelog</h1>

        <p>A rough log of what changed and when. The site evolves in small waves — here's the trail.</p>

        <hr>

        <div class="entry">
          <span class="entry-date">2026-03-28</span>
          <div class="entry-title">Real postcard art lands</div>
          <p>Replaced SVG placeholders on the homepage with actual Draw Things generations. The four postcards — First Setup Routes, Tuning the Claws, Which Claw, and Community Currents — now show real AI-generated artwork in that late-50s automotive travel poster style.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="entry">
          <span class="entry-date">2026-03-23</span>
          <div class="entry-title">Postcard rack arrives</div>
          <p>Transformed the homepage from a standard landing page into a flip-card rack. Each card addresses a different question: which project to pick, how to start, how to tune it, or where the community gathers.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="entry">
          <span class="entry-date">2026-03-21</span>
          <div class="entry-title">Site launch</div>
          <p>First public commit. Basic structure: homepage, route planner, recommendations, and community page. The aesthetic pulled from vintage travel postcards — cream, seafoam, Daphne blue.</p>
        </div>

        <hr>

        <p style="font-style: italic; color: var(--coffee); font-size: 0.95rem;">The beach is always shifting. More cards coming as the tide pulls out.</p>
      
        <footer style="margin-top: 2rem; padding-top: 1.5rem; border-top: 1px dashed rgba(109,74,56,0.15); text-align: center; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--coffee);">
          <p>🌊 crabbing since 2025 · <a href="/changelog/" style="color: var(--sea);">changelog</a> · <a href="https://github.com/mtdphn/crustaceans.sh" style="color: var(--sea);">source</a></p>
        </footer>

    </article>
  </div>

    <script>
      function toggleTheme() {
        const html = document.documentElement;
        const btn = document.querySelector('.theme-toggle');
        const isDark = html.classList.contains('dark');
        if (isDark) {
          html.classList.remove('dark');
          localStorage.setItem('theme', 'light');
          btn.textContent = '☀️';
        } else {
          html.classList.add('dark');
          localStorage.setItem('theme', 'dark');
          btn.textContent = '🌙';
        }
      }
      const saved = localStorage.getItem('theme');
      if (saved === 'dark' || (!saved && window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches)) {
        document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');
      }
      if (document.querySelector('.theme-toggle')) {
        document.querySelector('.theme-toggle').textContent = document.documentElement.classList.contains('dark') ? '🌙' : '☀️';
      }
    </script>
</body>
</html>